IdentityMappingUpdate

public IdentityMappingUpdate(long ts,
                             String signature)
Creates a new update mMapping for a given timestamp and signature. It is assumed that this peer is the initiator of the query and its address will be bound with the query as the destination for the result set.

Parameters:
ts - timestamp
signature - signature
